          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit has Tactical Doctrine or Assault Doctrine, it gains the following abilities:


Icy Calm: Reroll Resolve Tests of 1 made for this unit.


Veteran Linebreakers: After this unit’s Move step, select up to two enemy units within engagement range of this unit. The selected enemy units each suffer X Suppression where X is equal to the number of models in this unit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
