          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit is Activated, the closest visible enemy unit gains the following ability until the End step. If two or more units are the closest enemy unit, you choose which one of those units gains it until the End step.


Warmaster: For each ranged attack that targets this unit made by an enemy unit with Assault Doctrine, a Wound Roll of 6 causes an additional hit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Saltire of Madness" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="ed21-752f-bfd7-1bce">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While any enemy units are visible to this unit, it cannot capture objectives.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
