        <profile name="Relentless Exuberance" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="7ac1-346d-531c-f75d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">For each initiative roll you make, if an enemy unit is visible to this unit, add 1 D6 to that roll and discard the lowest result. If you do, the next time you select a unit to activate, you must select any of your BLOOD CLAWS units.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Howling Charge" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="fd54-8b6b-5d16-db53">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit has Assault Doctrine, after this unit finishes an Advance within engagement range of any enemy units, all enemy units within 6” of this unit suffers 2D3 Suppression.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
