            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit has Assault Doctrine, for each melee attack this unit makes which targets an enemy unit that is not ready, a successful Hit Roll of 5+ causes an additional hit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Hunter’s Discipline" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="af50-d2b3-bd3f-fc4a">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit has Tactical Doctrine, for each ranged attack this unit makes, that attack gains Suppressive X where X is equal to its D.</characteristic>
