          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select a point anywhere on the battlefield visible to and up to 24” away from this unit and draw a line along the battlefield between that paint and this unit. All enemy units along that line suffer D3+1 SW.</characteristic>
