            <characteristic name="D" typeId="c2c0-3714-05e2-65a0">4</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Abilities" typeId="d93f-70ee-72bc-5ef9">Breach, Once per turn, after a successful Wound Roll for an attack made for this weapon, select another enemy unit within 6” of and visible to the target unit of that attack. The selected enemy unit suffers 4+3D3 SW.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
