        <profile name="2 The Armour of Russ" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="true" id="d77f-1da6-2e32-96ec">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">This unit gains Resilient 6+ and for each Resilient Rolls made for this unit, you may reroll the result. After an enemy unit Activates within engagement range of this unit, that enemy unit suffers 2D3 Suppression.</characteristic>
