        <profile name="3 The Wulfen Stone" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="true" id="379d-7c0c-60f4-1088">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit Activates, you may ‘release the raging spirit’. If you do, this unit gains the following ability until the next time this unit Activates: Raging Spirit:


● You may reroll Move Rolls made for this unit.
● For each melee attack this unit makes, a Hit Roll of 6 causes an additional hit.
● This unit cannot capture objectives.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
          <modifiers>
            <modifier type="set" value="false" field="hidden">
              <conditions>
