            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit has Tactical Doctrine or Devastator Doctrine, it gains the following abilities:


Icy Calm: Reroll Resolve Tests of 1 made for this unit.


Veteran Instincts: For each ranged attack that targets this unit, if it is in cover for that attack, reroll Saving Throws of 1 for that attack.</characteristic>
