          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">Once per battle round, after this unit is Activated, you may &apos;report enemy positions&apos;. If you do, this unit becomes ready, skip this turn&apos;s Move and Attacks steps, then take another turn. During that turn, while selecting targets for your other units&apos; ranged weapons, you may select enemy units within 24” of and visible to this unit from an additional 4” away.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
