      <profiles>
        <profile name="Predatory Howl" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="4c17-2b9e-ac69-c5f6">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit has Assault Doctrine, each friendly unit within 16” gains the following ability:


Fenrys Hjølda!: For each melee attack this unit makes, a Hit Roll of 6 for that attack causes an additional hit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Shield Wall" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="a35f-e6aa-f0a5-c40d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit has Tactical Doctrine and is within 2” of and visible to another of your infantry units, this unit and other infantry units within 2” of and visible to this unit gain the following ability:

Skjaldborg: For each wound that a model in this unit is selected to suffer, roll a D6. On a 5+, that attack fails.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile typeId="55da-e0a0-1fa3-2d1c" typeName="Leader" hidden="false" id="984d-343d-5874-7b8f">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Must Attach to" typeId="2c63-5e3f-9132-459d">This unit must attach to either:
a) TACTICAL SQUAD
b) INTERCESSORS
c) ASSAULT INTERCESSORS
d) BLOOD CLAWS
e) GREY HUNTERS</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
