            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit is Activated, each enemy unit visible to and further than 10&quot; from this unit gains Hunter&apos;s Mark until the End step:


Hunter&apos;s Mark: After an enemy unit with Thundering Charge finishes an Advance, if that unit passed within 1&quot; of this unit during that Advance, this unit suffers 3 SW.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
