            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit has Assault Doctrine, after an enemy unit dies from an attack made for a Flame Projector equipped to a model in this unit, before removing that enemy unit from the battlefield, each enemy unit within 2D6” of that unit suffers 2 SW.</characteristic>
